00:24.000 --> 00:28.000
Lights over the Amazon, beams from the sky.

00:28.000 --> 00:32.000
A creature with red eyes and skin that's lethal to the touch.

00:36.000 --> 00:42.000
There's no one better to walk us into that mystery than today's guest, Aldo Ribello.

00:44.000 --> 00:49.000
Brazil's former minister of defense, current presidential candidate,

00:49.000 --> 00:53.000
and a man who's spent decades at the center of Brazilian power.

00:53.000 --> 00:57.000
A man who's probably seen firsthand into the UFO vault.

00:57.000 --> 01:04.000
